{
  "stem": "942.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just want to backtrack for a second.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This Death March-- why it was called a Death March because many thousands that could not walk anymore and we just had to drop them on the side of the road.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as the SS guards who were guarding us on each side, you know, before they left anybody behind, they shot them in the head.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were not-- they were not leaving anybody alive behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And many thousands were lost just through these death marches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we'll go forward to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I'm going up to the camp, passing the quarries, and these were prisoners from Mauthausen-- Jewish prisoners, mainly-- that were cutting these rocks in the middle of the winter in this quarry.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I could see these steps-- I don't know, about a hundred steps-- going up to the top.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were working on the side of this face of this cliff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it looked like a very bad place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was lucky that I didn't have to stay in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went into the camp, and there were thousands of us crammed in from all these different transports because, at this time, there were transports coming from all over in the east into Austrian camps.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were taken to the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] showers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to get undressed, so the few pieces of good clothes that I had, I lost it all.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went through the showers and came out again on the other side just with my boots on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, in fact, I was there for four days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for three days, they didn't know what to do with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were sitting in these barrack rooms, naked, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
